r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> player <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> team_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">AND</span> backnumber <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>사용할 인덱스 테이블의 결정은 RDBMS의 optimizer가 적절하게 결정</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"명시적으로-사용할-인덱스-테이블-결정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%85%EC%8B%9C%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EA%B2%B0%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"명시적으로 사용할 인덱스 테이블 결정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>명시적으로 사용할 인덱스 테이블 결정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>optimizer가 적절하게 결정하지 못할 경우 명시적으로 사용할 인덱스 테이블을 개발자가 결정</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">USE INDEX</code> : 사용할 인덱스 테이블 권장</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"83334743382320370000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`SELECT * FROM player USE INDEX (index_name) WHERE team_id = 1; -- index_name 사용 권장`, `83334743382320370000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> player <span class=\"token keyword\">USE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INDEX</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>index_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> team_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- index_name 사용 권장</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">FORCE INDEX</code> : 사용할 인덱스 테이블 강제</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"81129749148852140000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`SELECT * FROM player FORCE INDEX (index_name) WHERE team_id = 1; -- index_name 사용 강제`, `81129749148852140000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> player <span class=\"token keyword\">FORCE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INDEX</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>index_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> team_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- index_name 사용 강제</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">IGNORE INDEX</code> : 제외할 인덱스 테이블 명시</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"57131582901408915000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`SELECT * FROM player IGNORE INDEX (index_name) WHERE team_id = 1; -- index_name 사용 제외`, `57131582901408915000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> player <span class=\"token keyword\">IGNORE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INDEX</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>index_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> team_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- index_name 사용 제외</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"인덱스-단점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"인덱스 단점 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인덱스 단점</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>table에 튜플이 추가되면 인덱스 테이블에도 추가되고 정렬되므로 오버헤드 발생(인덱스 테이블 크기가 클수록 정렬에 오버헤드 발생)</li>\n<li>저장 공간 추가 필요</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"covering-index\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#covering-index\" aria-label=\"covering index permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>covering index</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>쿼리에 필요한 모든 컬럼이 인덱스에 포함된 경우 포인터 사용 없이 인덱스 테이블을 통해 쿼리 처리</li>\n<li>인덱스 테이블을 통해 쿼리 처리하므로 더 빠름</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/438ad64f-1953-4783-954f-c5a16d8092e8\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"hash-기반-인덱스\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hash-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4\" aria-label=\"hash 기반 인덱스 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hash 기반 인덱스</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hash table</code>을 사용하여 인덱스 테이블 생성</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">equality</code> 비교만 가능, <code class=\"language-text\">range</code> 비교 불가(이상, 이하 등 불가)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">multi-column</code> 인덱스는 사용한 모든 attribute에 대한 조회에만 활용 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"인덱스-참고-사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"인덱스 참고 사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인덱스 참고 사항</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>인덱스 활용보다 <code class=\"language-text\">full scan</code>이 더 빠른 경우가 있음\n<ul>\n<li>튜플이 적은 경우</li>\n<li>조회하려는 튜플이 테이블의 대부분을 차지하는 경우</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">full scan</code> vs <code class=\"language-text\">index scan</code> 또한 RDBMS의 optimizer가 적절하게 결정</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">foreign key</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">MYSQL</code>에서는 인덱스 자동 생성, <code class=\"language-text\">RDBMS</code>마다 다름</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">order by</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">group by</code>에도 활용 가능</li>\n<li>이미 데이터가 많은 테이블의 인덱스 생성시 시간이 오래 걸리고 DB 성능에 안좋은 영향을 끼칠 수 있음</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#db-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EB%9E%80\">DB 인덱스란</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#sql-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">SQL 인덱스 생성</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A1%B4%EC%9E%AC%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EC%9D%98-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">존재하는 테이블의 특정 속성에 대하여 인덱스 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%EC%8B%9C-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">테이블 생성시 인덱스 생성</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#sql-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C\">SQL 생성한 인덱스 조회</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#b-tree-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4\">B-Tree 기반 인덱스</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#a%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%BC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-a%EC%97%90%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C\"><code class=\"language-text\">a</code>컬럼 기준의 인덱스와 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>에대한 조건을 통한 조회</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#a%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%BC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-a-and-b%EC%97%90%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C\"><code class=\"language-text\">a</code>컬럼 기준의 인덱스와 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code> AND <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>에대한 조건을 통한 조회</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#a-b%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%BC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-a-and-b%EC%97%90%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C\"><code class=\"language-text\">{a, b}</code>컬럼 기준의 인덱스와 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code> AND <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>에대한 조건을 통한 조회</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#a-b%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%BC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-b%EC%97%90%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C\"><code class=\"language-text\">{a, b}</code>컬럼 기준의 인덱스와 <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>에대한 조건을 통한 조회</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#sql%EC%97%90-%EB%94%B0%EB%9D%BC-%EC%A0%9C%EB%8C%80%EB%A1%9C-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%B8%EC%A7%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">SQL에 따라 제대로 활용할 수 있는 인덱스인지 확인</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5-%EC%BF%BC%EB%A6%AC\">활용 가능 쿼리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B6%88%EA%B0%80-%EC%BF%BC%EB%A6%AC\">활용 불가 쿼리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%BF%BC%EB%A6%AC%EC%97%90-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EC%9D%B4-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4%EA%B1%B4%EC%A7%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">쿼리에 활용되는 인덱스 테이블이 어떤건지 확인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%AA%85%EC%8B%9C%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EA%B2%B0%EC%A0%95\">명시적으로 사용할 인덱스 테이블 결정</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EB%8B%A8%EC%A0%90\">인덱스 단점</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#covering-index\">covering index</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#hash-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4\">Hash 기반 인덱스</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\">인덱스 참고 사항</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"인덱스","date":"2025년 01월 21일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-21-인덱스/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-20-정규화/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"정규화","date":"2025-01-20 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-22-B-tree/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"B tree","date":"2025-01-22 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}